botLot

Class BotLot

  • java.lang.Object
    • botLot.BotLot

  • public class BotLot
extends java.lang.Object
    BotLot.java

    Holds the graph object and handles operations directly related with handling where it is in the graph, and moving around that graph.

    Started: 10/7/15

    Version:
    1.0 3/7/16
    Author:
